row.lpszDescrLong:
POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center Data Events Package
Contains the Data Events that are triggered by the College Adapter upon certain data changes to either built-in data tables or staging tables. Should not be customized by the College. Colleges should utilize the CCTC_COLLEGE_PKG to customize the code executed upon such events
